ting computational chemistry methods, both based on quantum\nmechanics and classical force fields, in particular in describing large and\nheterogeneous systems (ex. metalloproteins).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Sep 2016 16:51:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-22"}
