lar, the nature of\nultrahard X-ray protostellar candidates without known infrared counterparts\nneeds to be eludicated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Sep 2016 17:51:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Sep 2016 12:54:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
