ibit NEATM\nbeaming parameters that are lower than expected for a typical asteroid at all\nphase angles up to 100{\\deg}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Sep 2016 10:53:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-23"}
