o study the tails of these distributions. We also study\nreliability of this engine. We find the fluctuations dominate mean values of\nefficiency and COP and their probability distributions are broad with power law\ntails.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Sep 2016 11:59:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jul 2017 06:18:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-04"}
